                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980523-18-off91 t17980523-18-cd92"></join>, two pounds of brass tubes, value 3s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980523-18-victim193" type="victimName">
