                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980523-18-defend191 t17980523-18-punish96"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
